{"tid":1483704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果今晚有咩大穫嘢，就算今日3千萬人出黎都冇人理","createTime":"2019-08-18T12:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T14:29:49.000Z","uid":270423,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc0f6ee45461fcbd743efa39d02116c5ebc75c85","tid":1483704,"uid":270423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"冇錯我係P牌散水撚。<br />\n<br />\n根據以往經驗，特別係 8月5罷工個日，一入黑popo同黑社會搞事就會佔領晒網上討論同新聞，罷工罷成點、有幾多人，都冇人報冇人理。<br />\n<br />\n所以懇請在場手足要沉著應戰，唔好比今晚有咩事發生模糊咗焦點，要比世界知道今日係 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第三次超大型和理非百萬人集會！</span></span>"},{"pid":"604fe8dc3c15dfdfc05c59fc17a7ed4adea6f9b6","tid":1483704,"uid":270423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:51:10.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"9064292cd444ed5e18b7257a2485f7b145f1ca38","tid":1483704,"uid":273670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f671325edb2d7541b8707b3788cd737b427a4d","tid":1483704,"uid":270423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:53:20.000Z","msg":"同埋西環 狗已撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勇武手足快快沖熱水涼拒絕淋病"},{"pid":"727f3b8d402394c1bc34305dd4a8df591635fa52","tid":1483704,"uid":270423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:56:23.000Z","msg":"啱啱先出到嚟嘅歡迎你地去<span style=\"color: red;\">夜遊維園</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedaaaa70fd459f4ec5492a71eec62b9a48481e4","tid":1483704,"uid":270423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T12:58:30.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"9672fb0887d3c